			<h1>Content Model</h1>

        <h3>What is a Content Model?</h3>
        <p>A Content Model is a framework for understanding how to build content for pages in a website. It is the result of business requirement definition and design decisions. It captures several elements that make up the digital experience:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Page templates</li>
          <li>Components that make up each template</li>
          <li>Attributes of each component</li>
          <li>Intent, logic and rules for page templates, components and attributes</li>
        </ul>


